&lt;h2 id=&quot;list-of-errata&quot;&gt;List of errata&lt;a role=&quot;presentation&quot; class=&quot;anchor&quot; href=&quot;#list-of-errata&quot; title=&quot;Anchor link to this header&quot;&gt;#&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;
